 internet landscape, where malware, trackers, and phishing sites are rampant, this added layer of defense is extremely helpful.\u003c/p\u003e    \n\u003cp\u003eNordVPN is already one of the \u003ca href=\"https://www.makeuseof.com/security-apps-protect-your-data/\" target=\"_blank\"\u003etop security apps for protecting \u003c/a\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.makeuseof.com/security-apps-protect-your-data/\" target=\"_blank\"\u003edata\u003c/a\u003e, and its Threat Protection feature further enhances its usefulness.\u003c/p\u003e    \u003ch3 id=\"robust-malware-and-virus-protection\"\u003e\n            1. Robust Malware and Virus Protection\n    \u003c/h3\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eThe biggest reason to use Threat Protection is its anti-malware and antivirus capabilities. It runs in the background and automatically blocks access to malware-hosting websites. Additionally, it scans downloaded files for viruses and, if needed, uploads them to the cloud for deeper analysis.\u003c/p\u003e    \n\u003cp\u003eA key thing to note is that it only uploads executable files for further scanning if the quick scan doesn\u0026#39;t yield satisfactory results. Other files are scanned using the local scanner for privacy reasons.\u003c/p\u003e    \n\u003cp\u003eIf a file is found unsafe, it\u0026#39;s removed as soon as possible before it can harm your device. This is particularly useful, since getting rid of malware can be complex and time-consuming. While you can manually \u003ca href=\"http://www.makeuseof.com/how-remove-malware-from-computer-before-factory-reset/\" target=\"_blank\"\u003eremove malware from your device\u003c/a\u003e, Threat Protection saves you from that hassle.\u003c/p\u003e    \n\u003cp\u003eBecause of this proactive approach, Threat Protection is the first line of defense against cybersecurity threats like spyware, ransomware, Trojans, and worms.\u003c/p\u003e            \n    \n                    \n                        \n    \n    \n                            